{"tid":354084,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"8月尾青森3日","createTime":"2017-08-10T06:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T11:54:10.000Z","uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a08616e6d629cbf61501f2429be5f5635ab3701","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有好提議(就算唔係青森都ok)?我會有張JR東日本・南北海道鐵路周遊券由洞爺湖同函館玩落東京,仲諗緊點玩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> o個3日嘅第一日應該朝早函館去八戶放低行李先,之後就乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奧入瀨,海女依d點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a9a9bb75721fe4e3faa0c9ba183878f093ce5a","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96712dfc0ce8998b504bd705172cfad11b013e5f","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf19657fc5be6d191f4f02066ed30221077d1463","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d9e17f1ec8d2bebf33f4bf6ec1079f11970cca","tid":354084,"uid":73231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"你會唔會租車？"},{"pid":"a0f3aa95f7f6b2fdd5041ef6cdb1ca089d8cd910","tid":354084,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b9a70a2b2eaeb96866d4f37afe195548bcfbf0df","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你會唔會租車？</blockquote><br />\n唔識揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2f8186f23828bbdaff6dd46d8d0f9e858514ff","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"我未知第一日點算,第2日如果去奧入瀨都唔知邊度入邊度出好,唔知要行幾耐好怕miss巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,第3日可能去海女o個度一日?"},{"pid":"eb8268c482a0427a3a9f78ec3f6bb929a13d4e0b","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你會唔會租車？</blockquote><br />\nbtw絲打你最尾去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次去東北毫無概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16</a>"},{"pid":"9693394101c80c458b5a7065018b65e41794f36d","tid":354084,"uid":6759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"一個人？"},{"pid":"4b7484a328052408a2b1cd0e38e2ff2fd32fdd13","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人？</blockquote><br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5318950019d6e7294bf51b44249292a9df1c04ba","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0764bed35284584c5637394c48ecbec23da194d","tid":354084,"uid":6759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:49:05.000Z","msg":"三日去唔到禁多地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你函館朝市完去行奧入賴係入面住一晩或出青森住"},{"pid":"d8ce88f7e2a5e39d2cfb4f87e7ae45ce4b4f00ba","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三日去唔到禁多地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你函館朝市完去行奧入賴係入面住一晩或出青森住</blockquote><br />\n3日係淨東北咋,3日唔包函館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e0dfc58ae335ad549145e0b053e4b07718e02f","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:52:51.000Z","msg":"依家諗到頭都大埋,冇車東北好撚難plan"},{"pid":"6c277f4c089a172769064f3979e6601b97f069b7","tid":354084,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你會唔會租車？</blockquote><br />\nbtw絲打你最尾去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次去東北毫無概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16</a></blockquote><br />\n有去青森同奧入瀨呀<br />\n好靚好值得去<br />\n希望你去好天<br />\n<br />\n函館一晚<br />\n去青森拎車 之後去奧入瀨一晚<br />\n行完去八戶住一晚還車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青森啲手信好似幾正可惜我冇留多過幾個鐘<br />\n奧入瀨你預冇咗一日 特別你要等巴<br />\n東北pass 好似唔包 不過印象中都算密<br />\n行完全條要五個鐘 我哋都係揀嚟行<br />\n<br />\n八食中心值得去<br />\n蕪島種差落大雨去唔到<br />\n個美食橫丁我哋食嗰間麻麻<br />\n<br />\n東北啲人好似英文麻麻 餐牌未必有英文<br />\n<br />\n其實三日有少少趕<br />\n下次會想慢慢遊<br />\n<br />\n我而家計劃緊九州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdaa2971fc4a0efdfa0b0af564cf2743cd71a450","tid":354084,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家諗到頭都大埋,冇車東北好撚難plan</blockquote><br />\n我見種差海岸附近好似有站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八戶線好似幾疏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c42e3ae973eb212aed46b34d18b47333727ca39","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你會唔會租車？</blockquote><br />\nbtw絲打你最尾去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次去東北毫無概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16</a></blockquote><br />\n有去青森同奧入瀨呀<br />\n好靚好值得去<br />\n希望你去好天<br />\n<br />\n函館一晚<br />\n去青森拎車 之後去奧入瀨一晚<br />\n行完去八戶住一晚還車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青森啲手信好似幾正可惜我冇留多過幾個鐘<br />\n奧入瀨你預冇咗一日 特別你要等巴<br />\n東北pass 好似唔包 不過印象中都算密<br />\n行完全條要五個鐘 <span style=\"color: red;\">我哋都係揀嚟行</span><br />\n<br />\n八食中心值得去<br />\n蕪島種差落大雨去唔到<br />\n個美食橫丁我哋食嗰間麻麻<br />\n<br />\n東北啲人好似英文麻麻 餐牌未必有英文<br />\n<br />\n其實三日有少少趕<br />\n下次會想慢慢遊<br />\n<br />\n我而家計劃緊九州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你行咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗住跟你行跟返個時間,冇車走就死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80da8c9bcced471f5cde2a329355d541afe7e4ed","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家諗到頭都大埋,冇車東北好撚難plan</blockquote><br />\n我見種差海岸附近好似有站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八戶線好似幾疏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀,但其實都唔知玩唔玩到1日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0f727d09e59682ab5e14b7bd3408786207103e","tid":354084,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你會唔會租車？</blockquote><br />\nbtw絲打你最尾去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次去東北毫無概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293578/page/16</a></blockquote><br />\n有去青森同奧入瀨呀<br />\n好靚好值得去<br />\n希望你去好天<br />\n<br />\n函館一晚<br />\n去青森拎車 之後去奧入瀨一晚<br />\n行完去八戶住一晚還車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青森啲手信好似幾正可惜我冇留多過幾個鐘<br />\n奧入瀨你預冇咗一日 特別你要等巴<br />\n東北pass 好似唔包 不過印象中都算密<br />\n行完全條要五個鐘 <span style=\"color: red;\">我哋都係揀嚟行</span><br />\n<br />\n八食中心值得去<br />\n蕪島種差落大雨去唔到<br />\n個美食橫丁我哋食嗰間麻麻<br />\n<br />\n東北啲人好似英文麻麻 餐牌未必有英文<br />\n<br />\n其實三日有少少趕<br />\n下次會想慢慢遊<br />\n<br />\n我而家計劃緊九州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你行咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗住跟你行跟返個時間,冇車走就死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢巴士去八戶一日得3班,一miss就可能要坐去青森<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27204229d05d77c3826a0fc8ca9671d893e1a35d","tid":354084,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家諗到頭都大埋,冇車東北好撚難plan</blockquote><br />\n我見種差海岸附近好似有站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八戶線好似幾疏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀,但其實都唔知玩唔玩到1日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成兩個鐘班你都急唔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9502424ab8210fa971cdb5adecf92d884162178a","tid":354084,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你會唔會租車？</blockquote><br />\